            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-12-31T14:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-10-13T00:00:00+08:00" n="894" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d894">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Arrangements were made in the first quarter of 1949 for evacuation of several
                    thousand refugees from Shanghai. These included about 5,000 given temporary
                    haven in the Philippines and others sent via the United States to other
                    destinations. Some 1300 Russian emigrants remained as of April 1949 in
                    Shanghai.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
